### Create Service Request
POST https://sda-production-4678.up.railway.app/api/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": 3,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "address": "Karachi Pakistan",
  "bookingDate": "2026-06-10",
  "bookingTime": "10:00:00",
  "issueDescription": "Kitchen pipe leakage"
}

### Assign Worker
POST https://sda-production-4678.up.railway.app/api/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceRequestId": 1,
  "workerId": 2
}

### Get Request
GET https://sda-production-4678.up.railway.app/users/admin/




### Start Work
PUT https://sda-production-4678.up.railway.app/api/requests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}


### Complete Work
PUT https://sda-production-4678.up.railway.app/api/requests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}


